{"tid":1545192,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解班老師唔明 學生罷課唔係要你比壓力學生 而係政府","createTime":"2019-09-05T23:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:44:00.000Z","uid":48873,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bed75de156c8fec26def12ed23273180611603c4","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:45:14.000Z","msg":"831太子站真相必須cctv!<br />\n<br />\n求下你班仲有良知既老師<br />\n就算學校幾藍都好<br />\n你扮到好為學生著想 比壓力校長<br />\n再叫聽校長比壓力政府<br />\nd學生既行動先有更大作用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果可以嘅話 邊個唔想係課堂嘆冷氣？<br />\n唔好只係責怪/讚嘆年輕人<br />\n老師們都要出一分力 出多句聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你出句聲唔會死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72baa618366729089aafa03d642e083cab0625ef","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:45:38.000Z","msg":"試問誰還未發聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703fccba3f894a30f1b0b95fd5b28b2f9941fd13","tid":1545192,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8033610a4d2bf6d6584aa606d8dee54e26e73d74","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:47:22.000Z","msg":"大人要行多幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比d學生搭曬傳媒焦點先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474181f0a16fe364aac785ec750ae06672555380","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:48:24.000Z","msg":"我敢講 如果有間學校 老師同學生一齊組成人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 下年d人一定搶住入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e460b5d71463e3723a8fc1595b6bbb9af211617","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"教育局出張通告就係禁你言<br />\n你比咩缺點大過班學生都係想禁佢地言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班學生都唔驚，你驚？"},{"pid":"a9f014a07e3b006caac7fdc85e047e9d474711d5","tid":1545192,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:50:43.000Z","msg":"因為政府俾壓力學校囉"},{"pid":"d6dcedb68d4042de4ea022095ae710728688ffc2","tid":1545192,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"明既就唔會係教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0da7eef7bee2e35dbdca53b0e3ed3a6d54b29be","tid":1545192,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:51:26.000Z","msg":"打爆眼 打斷骨嘅市民<br />\n你身為老師 有無憐炆之心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有嘅話 出一份力 令政府多d壓力<br />\n<br />\n多你一個出聲 多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b70310063de589b32512c82d1456e1022d6741","tid":1545192,"uid":102700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"教畜又係淨係識恰細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd701e11d561fa57f743bef6d7427945276f865c","tid":154